{"tid":2023651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈如何突破樽頸","createTime":"2020-05-19T06:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T12:25:25.000Z","uid":61886,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"63b10dcd1b85fd1780a1b2d2a7a1e70cc73de3a2","tid":2023651,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"黨媒評擊<br />\n1. 商店不應分黃藍政見<br />\n2. 服務、質素及價錢決定顧客去留<br />\n3. 黃店大多小店，沒有力與大規模連鎖店比併<br />\n4. 供應鏈亦在中國，例如食材等。<br />\n就以上四點，除左第一點之外，另外三點我都大致認同，依三點亦都說明左黃圈既樽頸位，以下有少少我自己既意見。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>餐廳係最容易成為黃店及受支持</ins></strong><br />\n1. 大部份人對食物要求並不是太高，好既一餐，唔好既一餐，所以可以喺食果一方面完全支持黃色食店 (例如龍門)。<br />\n2. 但對比其他類型，好難做到依個效果，例如時裝店告急，主要係賣女裝日系服飾，target customer既比例比起食店已經低好多，就算佢係黃店，都會因為佢本身賣既產品唔係你既style而卻步；同樣，服務行業亦有相似情況 (例如gel甲)。<br />\n3. 所以，依類型既店舖係非常需要用質素去維持生計，如果希望好似食店既形式生存，就未免諗錯方向。(PS 當你搵到一間你鐘意既衫鋪又係黃既，就真係要多多懲罰)<br />\n4. 售賣產品類型的黃店，嘗試多與光時、Jimmy、重光號等合作，既然佢地有相應既平台，當然做到互惠互利更好，合作絕對是1+1&gt;2。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>黃店多為小店</ins></strong><br />\n1. 如何由小店變成連鎖店，好睇黃店老細既功力，襯住抗爭既熱度，適時擴充。<br />\n2. 個人認為，大渣哥等絕對有力開設10間以上。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>供應鏈主要在中國</ins></strong><br />\n1. 其實依個唔會係一個問題，就算退一百步咁講，到第時香港獨立，亦少不免會與中國有經貿來往，一買一賣，正常不過。 (個人當然支持本土農業及抵制MIC)<br />\n2. 以食店為例，亦可思考向上游發展，例如食物工場等等。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>黃店是否應該做藍絲生意</ins></strong><br />\n1. 商業角度而言，target customer愈多，生意亦會較好。<br />\n2. 貼滿文宣自然會少左一班藍絲幫襯，如何取得平衡確實需要思考。<br />\n3. 賺藍絲錢去支援同路人確實非常吸引。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>黃店顧客的投入</ins></strong><br />\n1. 幫襯是基本，不多說；個人感受，有部份黃店於運作規劃或質素等也有改善空間，嘗試向老細提出意見，當然是以善意的態度；一味盲目死撐，最終也只會亡於質素之下。<br />\n2. 除餐廳外，多了解其他行業的黃店，例如整車、整電話、盤裁等等。<br />\n<br />\n其實打完成篇，都覺得無咩point，當廢up下吹水，歡迎討論。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17665127f6d5b4de2755d3c3f5f60492e0d5701","tid":2023651,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"要搞B2B，唔好淨係B2C"},{"pid":"6be4239b6160b9284f933000c2c56d2d8da43559","tid":2023651,"uid":49151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:41:04.000Z","msg":"捐錢 <br />\n有幾多間而家仲捐緊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95f7e68c67d439109b5df2a9e5879188003c167","tid":2023651,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef964dd8816535302826149f74d9c6743ad27e9d","tid":2023651,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"講真, 我覺得要搞到有間黃店上市先可以突破樽頸, 但當中一定有好多惡意中傷!"},{"pid":"f806b8b306ccf6b1471df16a068b9b1409fef98c","tid":2023651,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d17665127f6d5b4de2755d3c3f5f60492e0d5701","tid":2023651,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"要搞B2B，唔好淨係B2C"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"餐廳就一定b2c<br />\nb2b真係要等龍門幾間做大個brand<br />\n再有力有心染指其他行業先得"},{"pid":"22625684558c21e600a1d21a9fb28e765f977f26","tid":2023651,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef964dd8816535302826149f74d9c6743ad27e9d","tid":2023651,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"講真, 我覺得要搞到有間黃店上市先可以突破樽頸, 但當中一定有好多惡意中傷!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"係 <br />\n餐廳黎講我最有期望係大渣哥<br />\n<br />\n光時都好有potential"},{"pid":"ea2f3465f327ac43e71b492ad5523c702e3877ba","tid":2023651,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d63041b87bff94b4345374f54ea6c5d53a8e7baa","tid":2023651,"uid":80600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"60e0826960c0d34b362e9db1e8c05072987c9601","tid":2023651,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a39126d0894b029c4bcce8c9e5b5b253c2e566","tid":2023651,"uid":106929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f806b8b306ccf6b1471df16a068b9b1409fef98c","tid":2023651,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d17665127f6d5b4de2755d3c3f5f60492e0d5701","tid":2023651,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"要搞B2B，唔好淨係B2C"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"餐廳就一定b2c<br />\nb2b真係要等龍門幾間做大個brand<br />\n再有力有心染指其他行業先得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:54:02.000Z","msg":"都要慢慢扶植各行各業 由細變大<br />\nB2B 要更有實力先做到"},{"pid":"455d8c1ec545e496e36cd1cfb186eef68fb96791","tid":2023651,"uid":300783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:54:06.000Z","msg":"要持續黃圈就要有實質推動力去推動消費，唔可以只靠情感<br />\n<br />\n【值得表揚】藍絲用黃店積分APP儲分<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2023549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2023549</a>"},{"pid":"500c353f44d1b577444b57723a7d7430ab6799c4","tid":2023651,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5357e6344b59ee687438d0289f7c1c87379990cb","tid":2023651,"uid":60589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"除左衣食住行，醫療都係一個必要開支，甚至保險等等。<br />\n不過個人認為首先必須撇除不停批鬥、人血饅頭，如果唔係門檻越黎越高根本就係趕同路人。每人每間鋪都會有自己嘅顧慮同難處，一味屌根本冇幫助。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8348eb401b88f9fa10b14747158c85695d96d5db","tid":2023651,"uid":159128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:00:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac3ad09296478de4bdd292761a35f112752cd21c","tid":2023651,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"美國公開多謝香港人<br />\n<br />\n史墨客：COVID-19抗疫之戰<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我們對兩地人民的深厚友誼，亦表謝意。許多香港人和美國人互相寄運口罩及其他醫療物資予對方。兩地人民及政府，一次次互相伸出友誼之手，協力應對全球挑戰。<br />\n<br />\nWe also appreciate the close ties of friendship between our two peoples. Many Hongkongers and Americans are shipping masks and other medical supplies to each other. Time and again, we have seen our people and our governments cooperate in friendship to overcome global challenges.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中文：<a href=\"https://hk.usconsulate.gov/zhhk/cg-2020051801-zh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.usconsulate.gov%2Fzhhk%2Fcg-2020051801-zh%2F&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=4558c1c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.usconsulate.gov/zhhk/cg-2020051801-zh/</a><br />\nEnglish：<a href=\"https://hk.usconsulate.gov/cg-2020051801/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.usconsulate.gov%2Fcg-2020051801%2F&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=3778381d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.usconsulate.gov/cg-2020051801/</a>"},{"pid":"a27f48875a4125f21df261cb2139c9850162553e","tid":2023651,"uid":37990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:03:48.000Z","msg":"1. 提升到國際層面，投資海外實業去支持本土，最初目標係減少對支那既依賴<br />\n<br />\n2. 拉籠本地商界（有機會係建制），例如將黃店集中係某d 冇咁親政府既地産商商場，零售類（例如hktvmall)一係就係咁科水幫襯，一係就造大新興網購（光時、Armubuy、重光），令佢地覺得香港本土生意有得做<br />\n<br />\n3. 黃店冇潔癖，會招呼藍絲<br />\n講真心話，我明真係會經營困難，但黃店下下都告急，其實黃圈資源係有限，汰弱留強係正常，你平靚正先係會吸引班只顧利益既藍絲幫襯，咁先藍錢入黃圈"},{"pid":"d0c468ac986244f7905fa6350f44160d37ef6a2f","tid":2023651,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"中國唔滅國點香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274eb211f19c9751da39747f700e1c340c21db32","tid":2023651,"uid":147182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:05:09.000Z","msg":"擴大黃色經濟圈<br />\n納入元氣 starbucks mcd等戒唔到既食店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3f344880e6a16b41dcbc80d8a50fa611d5111f","tid":2023651,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"22625684558c21e600a1d21a9fb28e765f977f26","tid":2023651,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef964dd8816535302826149f74d9c6743ad27e9d","tid":2023651,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"講真, 我覺得要搞到有間黃店上市先可以突破樽頸, 但當中一定有好多惡意中傷!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"係 <br />\n餐廳黎講我最有期望係大渣哥<br />\n<br />\n光時都好有potential"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:27:24.000Z","msg":"我自己之前已出過post講見解<br />\n<br />\n其實市場上既知名網店都係起步階段<br />\n我建議香港人盡快在海外集資成立一間黃色主權基金<br />\n盡力開辦網店及物流公司<br />\n盡量做到價廉物美，種類多，入貨盡量從東南亞及本地<br />\n網站種類，形式，設計，運作，<br />\n可參考競爭對手: 淘寶，美團，支付寶<br />\n同本地黃色網商可盡量合作<br />\n重振香港科研同經濟<br />\n長遠重可以開發埋用美金結算既手機支付系統<br />\nP牌推唔到，如認同請幫推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1794263/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1794263/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9af5363b3becbeef6dc1396172d70150ba8e6d23","tid":2023651,"uid":194588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:56:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"deea515aa3cab47a122f6786ebcd2f57fff246f9","tid":2023651,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c108360002ba95b61b7c7a77c1ce41f62faca3b","tid":2023651,"uid":7738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d3f344880e6a16b41dcbc80d8a50fa611d5111f","tid":2023651,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"22625684558c21e600a1d21a9fb28e765f977f26","tid":2023651,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef964dd8816535302826149f74d9c6743ad27e9d","tid":2023651,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"講真, 我覺得要搞到有間黃店上市先可以突破樽頸, 但當中一定有好多惡意中傷!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"係 <br />\n餐廳黎講我最有期望係大渣哥<br />\n<br />\n光時都好有potential"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:27:24.000Z","msg":"我自己之前已出過post講見解<br />\n<br />\n其實市場上既知名網店都係起步階段<br />\n我建議香港人盡快在海外集資成立一間黃色主權基金<br />\n盡力開辦網店及物流公司<br />\n盡量做到價廉物美，種類多，入貨盡量從東南亞及本地<br />\n網站種類，形式，設計，運作，<br />\n可參考競爭對手: 淘寶，美團，支付寶<br />\n同本地黃色網商可盡量合作<br />\n重振香港科研同經濟<br />\n長遠重可以開發埋用美金結算既手機支付系統<br />\nP牌推唔到，如認同請幫推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1794263/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1794263/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"好片面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bf86bb4e629bcd3a177671facfdb80695ed2b3","tid":2023651,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6be4239b6160b9284f933000c2c56d2d8da43559","tid":2023651,"uid":49151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:41:04.000Z","msg":"捐錢 <br />\n有幾多間而家仲捐緊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"1%都冇啦<br />\nd人食黃店當支持左手足 心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持老闆渣"},{"pid":"a959d32092f49a2d89eb39caab60f7c960c35d4c","tid":2023651,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}